// (ColorSnap)[http://snapyourcolors.com/]
// (Coolors)[https://coolors.co/image-picker]
// (unDraw)[https://undraw.co/]
// (References)[https://uxplanet.org/the-4-master-artists-who-used-nature-inspired-color-palettes-c10441c1c7d2]
